XPCC - Cross Platform Component Communication

Packet orientated communication library, enabling transparent communication 
between components on PCs and microcontrollers. It provides an interface to 
communicate via CAN, TCP/IP or TIPC.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
= INDEX =

 1. How to build the API-documentation 
 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
= 1. How to build the API-documentation =

You need Doxygen (http://www.doxygen.nl/).
Go to the src folder and invoke doxygen with
	xpcc/trunk/src$ doxygen ../doc/doxyfile
The documentation will be wrote to xpcc/trunk/doc/apidoc/html/
Start the index.html with your favourite browser.